{"tid":1890213,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"無通車效應！啟德1號(II)一房戶劈價逾200萬蝕沽","createTime":"2020-02-21T05:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T09:41:00.000Z","uid":62935,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"478867668298515c91a8f68c71b05aba543c72af","tid":1890213,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:14:40.000Z","msg":"港鐵屯門線通車，難敵疫情對樓市打擊，九龍啟德1號(II)錄帳面貶值個案。香港置業譚征表示，該盤3座高層單位，實用面積375方呎，一房間隔，曾叫價980萬港元放盤，其後持續減價，上月降價至850萬元，本月再減至780萬元，終以約765萬元沽出，呎價20,400元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">據了解，上址原業主持貨僅約3年，辣招鬆綁後即沽貨，帳面貶值近1%。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚氏續稱，同區二手放盤，除開放式單位，開價未聞低於800萬元。而一房放盤叫價普遍亦近900萬元，故是次成交低於市價。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開左地鐵站反而劈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b88db0459a1563b1dc3032bf1474a5a7af0dcb","tid":1890213,"uid":71508,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:15:17.000Z","msg":"因為佢傻左"},{"pid":"edeca84f6234f430a62e77af20c3b9a27176a1ed","tid":1890213,"uid":98860,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"980萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3746b30ea3715492ee0fecbc7227c014d726ec3","tid":1890213,"uid":98860,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:17:44.000Z","msg":"1房980萬,會買既係咩人"},{"pid":"16665a411e2378e51b4949601a0cd2cf7491066e","tid":1890213,"uid":289708,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"700幾萬仲有人幫佢買咪算執到"},{"pid":"12211b35321c808d7dc66742b421a348db2bf8f4","tid":1890213,"uid":65335,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:43:01.000Z","msg":"隔離全部係鉛水邨支那殖民<br />\n仲有人接火棒咪算好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe625bd45a65b47582edbfb602c6bf2af0996a9","tid":1890213,"uid":76745,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"r